<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>IELTS Roadmap — 7 Tháng</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0e0f11;
  --surface: #16181c;
  --surface2: #1e2026;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border2: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  --text: #e8e6df;
  --muted: #7a7870;
  --muted2: #5a5852;

  --cambridge: #2a7fff;
  --cambridge-soft: rgba(42,127,255,0.12);
  --cambridge-glow: rgba(42,127,255,0.25);

  --grammar: #00c48c;
  --grammar-soft: rgba(0,196,140,0.12);

  --mindset: #ff7043;
  --mindset-soft: rgba(255,112,67,0.12);

  --gold: #f5c842;
  --gold-soft: rgba(245,200,66,0.1);

  --p1: #5b8cff;
  --p2: #00c48c;
  --p3: #ff9800;
  --p4: #b06bff;

  --radius: 12px;
  --radius-sm: 8px;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Grid background */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 40px 40px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

.page { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 4rem; }

/* Header */
.header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.header-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cambridge); margin-bottom: 10px; }
.header-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 42px; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.header-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
.header-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 520px; }

/* Book legend */
.legend { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 7px 12px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border2); background: var(--surface); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
.legend-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.legend-item.cam { border-color: rgba(42,127,255,0.3); color: #7ab4ff; }
.legend-item.cam .legend-dot { background: var(--cambridge); }
.legend-item.gram { border-color: rgba(0,196,140,0.3); color: #5de3be; }
.legend-item.gram .legend-dot { background: var(--grammar); }
.legend-item.mind { border-color: rgba(255,112,67,0.3); color: #ffa07a; }
.legend-item.mind .legend-dot { background: var(--mindset); }

/* Tab switcher */
.tabs { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 2rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 4px; width: fit-content; }
.tab-btn { padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 7px; border: none; background: transparent; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s; }
.tab-btn.active { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border2); }
.tab-btn:hover:not(.active) { color: var(--text); }

/* View panels */
.view { display: none; }
.view.active { display: block; }

/* ===================== MONTHLY VIEW ===================== */
.timeline-bar { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
.tl-cell { padding: 14px 12px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s; }
.tl-cell::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; }
.tl-cell.p1::before { background: var(--p1); }
.tl-cell.p2::before { background: var(--p2); }
.tl-cell.p3::before { background: var(--p3); }
.tl-cell.p4::before { background: var(--p4); }
.tl-cell:hover { border-color: var(--border2); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.tl-months { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.tl-phase-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.tl-cell.p1 .tl-phase-name { color: var(--p1); }
.tl-cell.p2 .tl-phase-name { color: var(--p2); }
.tl-cell.p3 .tl-phase-name { color: var(--p3); }
.tl-cell.p4 .tl-phase-name { color: var(--p4); }
.tl-hours { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted2); }

/* Phase cards */
.phase-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); background: var(--surface); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
.phase-header { padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; }
.phase-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.phase-card.p1 .phase-icon { background: rgba(91,140,255,0.15); }
.phase-card.p2 .phase-icon { background: rgba(0,196,140,0.15); }
.phase-card.p3 .phase-icon { background: rgba(255,152,0,0.15); }
.phase-card.p4 .phase-icon { background: rgba(176,107,255,0.15); }
.phase-meta { flex: 1; }
.phase-badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.phase-card.p1 .phase-badge { background: rgba(91,140,255,0.15); color: #7ab4ff; }
.phase-card.p2 .phase-badge { background: rgba(0,196,140,0.15); color: #5de3be; }
.phase-card.p3 .phase-badge { background: rgba(255,152,0,0.15); color: #ffb74d; }
.phase-card.p4 .phase-badge { background: rgba(176,107,255,0.15); color: #ce93d8; }
.phase-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.phase-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }

.phase-body { padding: 16px 20px; display: grid; gap: 10px; }
.phase-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }

.book-block { border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 12px 14px; }
.book-block.cam { background: var(--cambridge-soft); border: 1px solid rgba(42,127,255,0.2); }
.book-block.gram { background: var(--grammar-soft); border: 1px solid rgba(0,196,140,0.2); }
.book-block.mind { background: var(--mindset-soft); border: 1px solid rgba(255,112,67,0.2); }
.book-block.all { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border2); }

.book-label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 7px; }
.book-label .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; }
.book-block.cam .book-label { color: #7ab4ff; }
.book-block.cam .dot { background: var(--cambridge); }
.book-block.gram .book-label { color: #5de3be; }
.book-block.gram .dot { background: var(--grammar); }
.book-block.mind .book-label { color: #ffa07a; }
.book-block.mind .dot { background: var(--mindset); }
.book-block.all .book-label { color: var(--muted); }
.book-block.all .dot { background: var(--muted); }

.book-content { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65; }
.book-content li { margin-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 12px; position: relative; }
.book-content li::before { content: '–'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--muted2); }

.goal-bar { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.goal-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; }
.goal-track { flex: 1; height: 4px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
.goal-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width .6s ease; }
.phase-card.p1 .goal-fill { background: var(--p1); }
.phase-card.p2 .goal-fill { background: var(--p2); }
.phase-card.p3 .goal-fill { background: var(--p3); }
.phase-card.p4 .goal-fill { background: var(--p4); }
.goal-band { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; }
.phase-card.p1 .goal-band { color: var(--p1); }
.phase-card.p2 .goal-band { color: var(--p2); }
.phase-card.p3 .goal-band { color: var(--p3); }
.phase-card.p4 .goal-band { color: var(--p4); }

/* ===================== WEEKLY VIEW ===================== */
.phase-selector { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.phase-sel-btn { padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); color: var(--muted); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s; }
.phase-sel-btn:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--border2); }
.phase-sel-btn.active { color: var(--text); }
.phase-sel-btn.active.p1 { background: rgba(91,140,255,0.15); border-color: rgba(91,140,255,0.4); color: var(--p1); }
.phase-sel-btn.active.p2 { background: rgba(0,196,140,0.15); border-color: rgba(0,196,140,0.4); color: var(--p2); }
.phase-sel-btn.active.p3 { background: rgba(255,152,0,0.15); border-color: rgba(255,152,0,0.4); color: var(--p3); }
.phase-sel-btn.active.p4 { background: rgba(176,107,255,0.15); border-color: rgba(176,107,255,0.4); color: var(--p4); }

.weekly-panel { display: none; }
.weekly-panel.active { display: block; }

.week-grid { display: grid; gap: 10px; }
.week-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); background: var(--surface); overflow: hidden; }
.week-header { padding: 11px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.week-num { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.week-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
.week-intensity { margin-left: auto; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; }

.week-body { padding: 12px 16px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 8px; }
.day-block { background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 7px; padding: 9px 11px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.day-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted2); margin-bottom: 5px; }
.day-item { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.day-item .src { font-size: 10px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 2px; }
.src.cam { background: var(--cambridge-soft); color: #7ab4ff; }
.src.gram { background: var(--grammar-soft); color: #5de3be; }
.src.mind { background: var(--mindset-soft); color: #ffa07a; }

.week-tip { margin: 0 16px 12px; padding: 9px 12px; background: var(--gold-soft); border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.2); border-radius: 7px; font-size: 11.5px; color: #e8d47a; line-height: 1.55; }
.week-tip strong { font-weight: 600; }

/* band target badge */
.band-target { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 8px; }

/* responsive */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .header-title { font-size: 30px; }
  .timeline-bar { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
  .phase-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .week-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* Animations */
@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(14px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
.phase-card, .week-card { animation: fadeUp .35s ease both; }
.phase-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: .05s; }
.phase-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .1s; }
.phase-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: .15s; }
.phase-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: .2s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-eyebrow">IELTS Academic · Band 4.0 → 6.5</div>
    <h1 class="header-title">Lộ trình <em>7 tháng</em><br>chinh phục IELTS</h1>
    <p class="header-sub">Kết hợp 3 bộ sách: Cambridge Guide · Grammar in Use · Mindset for IELTS · Tháng 4 – Tháng 12/2025</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Legend -->
  <div class="legend">
    <div class="legend-item cam"><span class="legend-dot"></span>The Official Cambridge Guide to IELTS</div>
    <div class="legend-item gram"><span class="legend-dot"></span>Grammar in Use (xanh dương)</div>
    <div class="legend-item mind"><span class="legend-dot"></span>Mindset for IELTS (Foundation + Level 1)</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tabs -->
  <div class="tabs">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('monthly')">Tổng quan tháng</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('weekly')">Chi tiết tuần</button>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ MONTHLY VIEW ============ -->
  <div class="view active" id="view-monthly">

    <div class="timeline-bar">
      <div class="tl-cell p1"><div class="tl-months">Tháng 4 – 5</div><div class="tl-phase-name">Nền tảng</div><div class="tl-hours">1–2h/ngày</div></div>
      <div class="tl-cell p2"><div class="tl-months">Tháng 6 – 8</div><div class="tl-phase-name">Chuyên sâu</div><div class="tl-hours">3–4h/ngày</div></div>
      <div class="tl-cell p3"><div class="tl-months">Tháng 9 – 10</div><div class="tl-phase-name">Luyện đề</div><div class="tl-hours">3–4h/ngày</div></div>
      <div class="tl-cell p4"><div class="tl-months">Tháng 11 – 12</div><div class="tl-phase-name">Giữ form</div><div class="tl-hours">1–2h/ngày</div></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Phase 1 -->
    <div class="phase-card p1">
      <div class="phase-header">
        <div class="phase-icon">📐</div>
        <div class="phase-meta">
          <span class="phase-badge">Giai đoạn 1 · Tháng 4–5</span>
          <div class="phase-title">Nền tảng — Hiểu cấu trúc & sửa lỗi cơ bản</div>
          <div class="phase-desc">Bận học trên lớp · Học 1–2 tiếng/ngày khi có thể · Không bỏ hẳn dù bận</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-grid">
          <div class="book-block cam">
            <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Cambridge Guide</div>
            <ul class="book-content">
              <li>Đọc IELTS Academic Summary toàn bộ (tuần 1 bắt buộc)</li>
              <li>Reading Unit 1–4: skimming, scanning, T/F/NG</li>
              <li>Speaking Unit 1–2: cấu trúc Part 1, nghe mẫu DVD</li>
              <li>Listening Unit 1–2: làm quen dạng bài</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="book-block gram">
            <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Grammar in Use</div>
            <ul class="book-content">
              <li>Unit 1–5: Present tenses (simple/continuous)</li>
              <li>Unit 6–10: Past tenses</li>
              <li>Unit 11–15: Future forms</li>
              <li>Unit 67–72: Articles (a/an/the) — lỗi cực phổ biến</li>
              <li>20 phút/ngày, mỗi ngày 1 unit nhỏ</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-block mind">
          <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Mindset for IELTS — Foundation</div>
          <ul class="book-content">
            <li>Unit 1–3: Vocabulary building theo chủ đề (Education, Work, Environment)</li>
            <li>Học Word Forms mỗi unit: noun / verb / adjective / adverb</li>
            <li>Speaking: luyện câu trả lời ngắn Part 1 theo Mindset Foundation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="goal-bar">
          <span class="goal-label">Mục tiêu cuối giai đoạn</span>
          <div class="goal-track"><div class="goal-fill" style="width:50%"></div></div>
          <span class="goal-band">Band 5.0</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Phase 2 -->
    <div class="phase-card p2">
      <div class="phase-header">
        <div class="phase-icon">🚀</div>
        <div class="phase-meta">
          <span class="phase-badge">Giai đoạn 2 · Tháng 6–8</span>
          <div class="phase-title">Chuyên sâu — Hoàn thành Skills Units & từ vựng học thuật</div>
          <div class="phase-desc">Nghỉ hè · 3–4 tiếng/ngày · Trọng tâm Reading + Speaking + Writing</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-grid">
          <div class="book-block cam">
            <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Cambridge Guide</div>
            <ul class="book-content">
              <li>Reading Unit 5–10: matching headings, sentence completion, diagram</li>
              <li>Writing Unit 1–6: Task 1 (charts/graphs) + Task 2 (essay structure)</li>
              <li>Speaking Unit 3–6: Part 2 cue card, Part 3 discussion</li>
              <li>Listening Unit 3–8: multiple choice, map labelling, flow chart</li>
              <li>Học kỹ "How to do it" trước mỗi unit</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="book-block gram">
            <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Grammar in Use</div>
            <ul class="book-content">
              <li>Unit 20–30: Modal verbs (can/could/may/might/should)</li>
              <li>Unit 31–40: If-clauses (conditional 1, 2, 3)</li>
              <li>Unit 41–50: Passive voice — quan trọng cho Writing Task 1</li>
              <li>Unit 80–90: Relative clauses — nâng cấp câu phức</li>
              <li>Unit 100–110: Comparison (as…as, more…than, the most)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-block mind">
          <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Mindset for IELTS — Foundation + Level 1</div>
          <ul class="book-content">
            <li><strong>Foundation Unit 4–8:</strong> Vocabulary theo chủ đề (Health, Technology, Society, Culture, Nature)</li>
            <li><strong>Level 1 Unit 1–5:</strong> Bắt đầu Academic vocabulary — synonyms, paraphrase practice</li>
            <li><strong>Writing:</strong> Dùng Mindset Level 1 để học cấu trúc Task 2 essay (opinion / discussion / problem-solution)</li>
            <li><strong>Từ cấm — thay thế:</strong> very → extremely/considerably, good → beneficial/effective, bad → detrimental, important → crucial/significant</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="goal-bar">
          <span class="goal-label">Mục tiêu cuối giai đoạn</span>
          <div class="goal-track"><div class="goal-fill" style="width:72%"></div></div>
          <span class="goal-band">Band 5.5 – 6.0</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Phase 3 -->
    <div class="phase-card p3">
      <div class="phase-header">
        <div class="phase-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="phase-meta">
          <span class="phase-badge">Giai đoạn 3 · Tháng 9–10</span>
          <div class="phase-title">Luyện đề — 8 Practice Tests + phân tích lỗi</div>
          <div class="phase-desc">Vẫn nghỉ hè · 3–4 tiếng/ngày · Điều kiện thi thật</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-grid">
          <div class="book-block cam">
            <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Cambridge Guide</div>
            <ul class="book-content">
              <li>Practice Test 1 trước (có hints & reminders)</li>
              <li>Tests 2–4: Academic Reading + Writing tập trung</li>
              <li>Tests 5–8: Full test đúng giờ không dừng</li>
              <li>Sau mỗi test: đọc kỹ Answer Key + giải thích</li>
              <li>Lỗi sai → quay lại đúng unit trong Skills Section</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="book-block gram">
            <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Grammar in Use</div>
            <ul class="book-content">
              <li>Ôn lại unit tương ứng lỗi sai trong Practice Tests</li>
              <li>Unit 46–55: Reported speech — quan trọng cho Listening</li>
              <li>Unit 111–120: Prepositions — lỗi nhỏ nhưng trừ band thật</li>
              <li>Không học unit mới — chỉ ôn và củng cố</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-block mind">
          <div class="book-label"><span class="dot"></span>Mindset for IELTS — Level 1</div>
          <ul class="book-content">
            <li><strong>Level 1 Unit 6–10:</strong> Luyện Speaking Part 2 theo chủ đề nâng cao (describe a place / person / experience / object)</li>
            <li>Dùng Mindset vocabulary lists để làm giàu bài Writing khi luyện đề</li>
            <li>Luyện paraphrase đề bài Task 2 — không chép lại từ đề</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="goal-bar">
          <span class="goal-label">Mục tiêu cuối giai đoạn</span>
          <div class="goal-track"><div class="goal-fill" style="width:88%"></div></div>
          <span class="goal-band">Band 6.0 – 6.5</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Phase 4 -->
    <div class="phase-card p4">
      <div class="phase-header">
        <div class="phase-icon">🏁</div>
